<br>
Attention True Adventurers  of norrath!<br>
<br>
A  new chapter in the history of the  world of Firiona Vie is being written and this is your chance not to be left out! For some time now our people have been overwhelmed with the discovery of new lands, new peoples, and new.. more powerful items to the point of exhaustion. Our community grows more strained and stretched by the day with some being forced to travel alone for most of their lives and some never knowing what it is like to have a true friend to laugh with .. to drink with .. to fight side by side with...<br>
<br>
Were you alive in the old times? When Kunark had just been discovered.. when the combine spires were the subject of great speculation for no one knew their purpose other then to serve as magical waypoints for wizards? When the world was simple and the twin dragons VOX and NAGAFEN were the pinnicle of might and there were few who opposed them? when you could leave the gates of qeynos, enter the qeynos hills and find  people with which you might fight with , learn with .. love with...<br>
<br>
Those times are gone.. like dust in the wind they have blown away to make way for &quot;progress&quot; .. what a bitter taste that word leaves.... and most  never know the majisty that is the old world and kunark. <br>
<br>
But while they may be gone for some.. they needent be gone for all! I propose getting together a grouping of adventurers from the various parts of the world to re discover the land that we once knew as the only home we had. NORRATH in all its glory and simplicity.  A friend of mine has written this message in not 0nly human, but in  all the languages known to the sentient races of norrath and luclin... even froglock which &lt;hopefully &gt; explains the great length of this paper.<br>
<br>
IF you beleve that you can hold yourself to the constraints of the old world of norrath &lt;other then initial transportation to the place of meeting which is TBA &gt;(&quot;to be announced&quot; for the less acronym minded of us) and are a  MATURE minded person (emphisis on MATURITY here) keen on living your life true to the path that you have chosen, then please sign your name on this sheet of paper where the space has been alotted.<br>
<br>
thank you  and good day<br>
<br>
(ooc) I would prefer that everyonethat does sign up sees themselves as a GOOD or at least Neutral Good aligned character and roleplays  to that degree. dark races are not minded so long as they pledge themselves to the light and at the very least fight the urges that push them to darkness.<br>
<br>
Understand that no items from any expansion other then kunark and the original everquest will be used if you decide to join this group.. also understand that we  will not be using any method of transportation other then old world transportation.IE no PoP ports , no Luclin ports. foods and such from the  expansions are welcome, though advanced tradeskill items such as armors, weapons, shields, and the like are not. (i couldnt say no to good food or drink.. everyone loves to have a misty thicket picnic every once in a while.. they're just so yummy!)<br>
<br>
so if you are interested.. please post and make it known. i would really like to get this group started and relive the old everquest glory before sony screwed everything up <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> .<br>
